'''Corax Ore''' was a valuable mineral found in the [[Kadal Asteroid Field]], near the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bestal Three]]. [[Fax Ventures]] mined the ore from the [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroids]] and processed it on the planet.

